Package: rbfmvar
Type: Package
Title: Residual-Based Fully Modified VAR Estimation
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Muhammad", "Alkhalaf", email = "muhammedalkhalaf@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-2677-9246"))
Description: Implements the Residual-Based Fully Modified VAR (RBFM-VAR)
    estimator of Chang (2000) <doi:10.1017/S0266466600166017> for vector
    autoregressive models that may contain an unknown mixture of I(0), I(1),
    and I(2) components. The procedure extends the Phillips (1995) FM-VAR by
    applying a nonparametric long-run variance correction to the OLS residuals,
    enabling valid inference without prior knowledge of the integration orders.
    Supports lag selection by AIC, BIC, and Hannan-Quinn criteria, modified
    Wald Granger non-causality tests, and impulse response functions.
Author: Muhammad Alkhalaf [aut, cre, cph]
    (<https://orcid.org/0009-0002-2677-9246>)
